data.description: Welcome to this impeccable move-in-ready home.  Located near downtown Margate off of Margate Blvd.  This 2 bedroom and 1 bathroom home is updated and waiting for you.  Updated, modern kitchen with quartz countertops.  The home has impact doors and windows throughout. Large hurricane-proof shed in back with well water for sprinkler system. Large outdoor space, automatic awning, with a fenced-in backyard with fruit trees waiting for you to pick and enjoy. No HOA makes this home an inviting property for potential buyers.  Don't hesitate, this home will not last long. Come and check out the Jewel on East River Drive.  Additional photos coming soon.
